flowchart LR
    subgraph Production["Production System"]
        NIC[Network Interface] --> XDP[XDP Filter]
        XDP -->|Drop| D[Dropped]
        XDP -->|Pass| KS[Kernel Stack]
        XDP -->|Redirect| TAP[Tap Interface]
    end

    subgraph Analysis["Analysis Layer"]
        TAP --> PCAP[libpcap Capture]
        PCAP --> FILE[pcap Files]
        KS --> APP[Application]
    end

    subgraph Dev["Developer Workstation"]
        CLI[CLI Tool] -->|libpcap| LOCAL[Local Analysis]
        CLI -->|Remote| APP
    end
